          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "道德沖融，應用不窮。淵深不可測量，為萬物之宗祖。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "hesonggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "挫銳解紛，和光同塵，皆謙退藏密之義。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "hesonggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "湛然常存，不知其誰之子，乃在天帝之先而生。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
